    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
      <head>Scope and Content</head>
      <p>The collection primarily documents the annual Loudoun History Awards Ceremony.  Images are individually catalogued in PastPerfect, Thomas Balch Library's visual collections database available onsite, and may be identified in the online index available at www.leesburgva.gov/ThomasBalchLibrary/SpecialCollections by searching vc_rg08. Photographs are not available for all years.</p>
